nodes.text: Beixander 9 was a small lonely moon located in the galaxy's Mid Rim. that was located in a quiet system within the galaxy. It was covered in oceans and hills, one of which was home to a settlement. Bazine Netal was directed to Beixander 9 after acquiring the Millennium Falcon from Hondo Ohnaka, but Mahjo Reeloo had incapacitated her real contact, taking the Falcon back to Ohnaka on Batuu.
